 &lt;p&gt;Obihai had officially announced Obi devices are supported by Google Voice. With a Google Voice account and a companion OBi device you can make and receive VoIP calls on a regular home phone. Obihai adapters have been around since 2011, with the latest update and the Google Voice official integration, the installation process is easier than before. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All you need is a Obi device (Obi100, Obi110, Obi200, Obi202), a good internet connection, a regular phone. Although you need to pay for the OBI device, after you pair it up with Google voice, you will save a lot from your phone bill every month. &lt;/p&gt;
